### Banking Transactions API - Sample Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or paste into curl

@host = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/health

### Create a Transfer Transaction
POST {{host}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Create a Deposit Transaction
POST {{host}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-00000",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create a Withdrawal Transaction
POST {{host}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-00000",
  "amount": 50.25,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### List All Transactions
GET {{host}}/transactions

### Get Specific Transaction (replace {id} with actual transaction ID)
GET {{host}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}

### Get Account Balance
GET {{host}}/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Get Another Account Balance
GET {{host}}/accounts/ACC-67890/balance

### Get Balance for Non-existent Account (should return 404)
GET {{host}}/accounts/ACC-99999/balance

### Get Non-existent Transaction (should return 404)
GET {{host}}/transactions/non-existent-id
